{"tid":207094,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街啦屌 箍完牙既既巴絲入","createTime":"2017-04-18T18:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T04:49:55.000Z","uid":7049,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae523496a902203e766384c1b5371b9ff437d3e9","tid":207094,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:09:32.000Z","msg":"屌 奶野啦 除左箍就快兩年 而家晚晚都會戴固定器<br />\n琴日奶野 除左放左係紙巾 唔小心快快手dum埋再倒埋垃圾 <br />\n<br />\n想問整返個固定器上下牙要幾錢<br />\n<br />\n我之前睇開個牙醫成日都唔係香港 <br />\n<br />\n聽日起身就要仆出去搵牙醫整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇知邊間會肯幫個唔係佢度箍既人整固定器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你地睇開邊個牙醫好都留一留名比我<br />\n我一間一間打去問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該晒你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a6ddee3d2ae41420ffabde95b3e487b94afa92","tid":207094,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:11:57.000Z","msg":"我知我開錯台 我都係希望多d人見到 sorry<br />\n自吞一堆膠先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e761260102db335b4c5b70ee680037a93dee25","tid":207094,"uid":51549,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T18:13:45.000Z","msg":"牙醫同我講小心保管，而家一對要4千"},{"pid":"fae